{"tid":2363531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林村許願節因疫情取消初一至初九活動","createTime":"2021-01-12T09:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T09:18:52.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6d2ac962003dc687004203493d22e026571be0b4","tid":2363531,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:18:52.000Z","msg":"大埔林村鄉委會主席林奕權表示，星期日經開會後決定，因應新型肺炎疫情嚴峻，將會取消新春年初一至初九的林村許願節活動，至於初十至正月十五能否重開，則要視乎疫情發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569987-20210112.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569987-20210112.htm&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJubXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=c255abd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569987-20210112.htm&h=daf53576\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569987-20210112.htm</a>"}]}